/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_UnitPrice" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_UnitPrice"
(
"UnitPriceID" INTEGER not null,
"PriceMethodCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"PriceMethodName" VARCHAR2(50) not null,
"OrderNum" INTEGER not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
constraint PK_CON_UNITPRICE primary key ("UnitPriceID")
);

comment on column "CON_UnitPrice"."PriceMethodCode" is
'10:比例
20:固定单价';

comment on column "CON_UnitPrice"."Enable" is
'1:有效 0：无效';
